item.title: 67th RBras and 20th SEAGRO will be held at Londrina/PR, Brazil
item.description: The 67th RBras and 20th SEAGRO will be held at the Events and Conventions Center of Aurora Shopping in the city of Londrina/PR, Brazil. The event will take place between July 24 and 28, 2023.
